(def about-exicon
  { :content [
              (p "At Exicon we believe in the power of mobile as a way of connecting companies with users.")
              (p "We know firsthand how long it takes to understand this highly fragmented industry and
                 how difficult it is for those not experienced in mobile to feel truly confident about what
                 decisions to make, and how to make them. ")
              (p "Our platform was therefore designed to help companies bring together all of their mobile
                 efforts while empowering their teams to be successful.")
              (p "The key problems that we aim to solve are:")
              (ul
                (li (b "\"How to find a great developer for my mobile project\"")(br)
                    "not just a list of the top developers but the best development companies for my idea,
                    my budget, my location, my industry and the features I want ")
                (li (b "\"How do I manage all the moving parts of mobile\"")(br)
                    "as marketing and product divisions across organisations run to meet demand for mobile
                    there is a need to address the shortage of brand standards, IP protection, best of breed
                    practices, the enormous duplication of effort and wasted resources.")
                (li (b "\"How do I address mobile as a channel to my customers and not simply a campaign\"")(br)
                    "not just the design of your mobile solution but also how you get in front of your users
                    while continuing to engage going forward."))
              (p "The AppBoard is a \"virtual advisor\", sitting at your shoulder, helping you make smart
                 decisions and guiding you through the entire journey -
                 from Build, to Manage, to Promote - the key stages
                 required to building quality connections with mobile users.")
              (h2 :class "ui medium header" "Be the mobile expert")
              ]})

(def timeline-description
  { :content [
              (p "Exicon was born in 2007 as a developer agency working with the world's leading mobile handset manufacturers.")
              (p "After 2 years we launched XDC, \"Exicon Developers Connect\" with a qualified network of over 3,000 mobile software
                 development companies for customers like Sony, Blackberry, Nokia, HP, Qualcomm, and Huawei.")
              (p "Next we built BAM! \"Branded App Matchmaker\" , an automated solution matching marketers and businesses across all
                 industries with qualified professional developers' based on skills, location, expertise, language and budget.")
              (p "To promote XDC and BAM! we partnered with local boutique agencies to pioneer app workshops in over 20 leading cities
                 around the world, bringing brand managers and mobile development specialists together to build engaging apps.")
              (p "Over time we realised that customers were struggling to and in some cases entirely absent. In order to save the
                 client money and streamline efficiencies moving forward, they needed help putting all these pieces together and
                 managing it from one place.")
              (p "It was then, in 2013, the AppBoard was born helping companies \"get a grip\" on their apps.")
              (p "Combined with our tools and workflows we aggregate and integrate all relevant mobile information so businesses can build,
                 manage and promote their mobile apps all from one location across an organization everywhere in the world.")
              (p "Our customers tap into our wealth of mobile experience having curated connections worth over 300M USD between our customers
                 and development companies while we continue to enhance our product with features for businesses both large and small or from
                 the app-preneur or the app-terprise to develop quality engagements with their mobile users.")]})

